                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#1va">Fol. 1va</locus>: Donation note. <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 1va: ዝቅዳሴ፡ ዘቂርቆስ፡ ሃራ፡ ዘተሰየጦ፡ ወልደ፡ ሥላሴ፡ ከሙት፡ ኵነኒ፡ መድኀኒተ፡ ነፍሴ፡ ኢትሕድጉኒ፡ ሥላሴ፡ ለዘላለም፡ ሥላሴ። ዘሰረቃ፡ ወዘፈሐቃ፡ ውጉዘ፡ ለይኩን፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም።</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol. 1va:  This missal of Qirqos Hara was purchased by Wäldä Śǝllase (so that it might be) salvation for my soul from condemnation to death. Don’t abandon me the Trinity forever the Trinity. May be condemned forever whoever steals it and erases it.</q>
                           
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#1va">Fol. 1va</locus>-vb: Donation note.<q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 1va-b: ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘወልደ፡ ሥላሴ፡ ዘወሀቦ፡ ለቅዱስ፡ ቂርቆስ፡ ወዘአጽሐፎ፡ አቡነ፡ ገብረ፡ ማርያም፡ ከመ፡ ይኩኖሙ፡ መርሃ፡ ለመንግሥተ፡ ሰማያት። ወአቡሁ፡ ወልደ፡ ሳሙኤል፡ ገብረ፡ ዋህድ፡ ዘርዓ፡ ጽዮን፡ ወእሙ፡ ወለተ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ ወለተ፡ ጽዮን፡ እምነ፡ ጽዮን፡ ወለተ፡ ኤልሳቤጥ፡ አመተ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ዘተጽሕፈት፡ በዘመነ፡ ንጉሥነ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ወጳጳስነ፡ አትናቴዎስ፡ ወቄስ፡ ገበዝ፡ ወልደ፡ ኪሮስ፡ ወባሕር፡ ነጋሲ፡ ተወልደ ᎓ መድኅን᎓ ወእኁሁ᎓ ወልደ᎓ ክርስቶስ᎓ ወአቡሆሙ᎓ ገብረ᎓ አደንያስ᎓ ወጸሐፊሃ᎓ አቡነ᎓ ወልደ᎓ ሙሴ።</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol. 1va-b: Let this book of Wäldä Śǝllase which he donated to the Saint Qirqos [Church] and which commissioned ʾabunä Gäbrä Maryam become a guide to the Kingdom of Heaven. And (for) his father Wäldä Samuʾel Gäbrä Wahǝd Zärʿa Ṣǝyon and his mother Wälättä Giyorgis, Wälättä Ṣǝyon, ʾƎmmǝnä Ṣǝyon, Wälättä ʾElsabeṭ, ʾAmätä Mikaʾel. It was written in the time of our king Yoḥannǝs and our metropolitan ʾAtnatewos and qesä gäbäz Wäldä Kiros and baḥr nägasi Täwäldä Mädḫǝn and his brother Wäldä Krǝstos and their father Gäbrä Adänyas and the scribe (is) Wäldä Muse.</q>
                           
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <locus target="#113rb">Fol. 113rb</locus>ls.9-21: Donation note.<q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 113rb ls.9-21: ዝቅዳሴ፡ ዘቂርቆስ፡ ሃራ፡ ዘወሀቦ፡ ወልደ፡ ሥላሴ፡ ወዘአጽሐፍዋ፡ አቡነ፡ ገብረ፡ ማርያም፡ ወጸሐፊሃ፡ አቡነ፡ ወልደ፡ ሙሴ፡ ዋጋ ፱ ብር᎓ ነው… </q>
                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol. 113rb ls.9-21: This missal of Qirqos Hara which donated Wäldä Śǝllase and which commissioned ʾabunä Gäbrä Maryam and wrote ʾabunä Wäldä Muse costs 9 bǝrr...</q>
                           The information about the price is in Amharic (9 Bǝrr).
The note indicates the names of the donor, the scribe, the commissioner (the same as in Additio 1 and 2) and the price for which the Ms. was purchased by the donor.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Notes in the upper margin: fols. 35r, 36r, 90v.&#xD;
- Notes in pen, within the main text field: fols. 101v, 102r.&#xD;
- Minor note (pen trial?): fol. 113v.&#xD;
- Short text; words are written without spaces or punctuation signs between them; its meaning is unclear, possibly an exercise in writing (cp. the initial words: ብርዕዘፈቲነ…): fol. 114r.&#xD;
- Pen trials: fols. 1r, 1v.</item>
